sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as sprawl CLI
    participant S as sprawl API
    participant B as Browser

    U->>C: sprawl login
    C->>S: POST /api/auth/device
    S-->>C: device_code, user_code, verification_uri_complete, interval, expires_in
    C-->>U: "open <url>, enter <user_code>"
    U->>B: Open URL, approve
    B->>S: Approve grant
    loop every `interval` seconds
        C->>S: POST /api/auth/device/token {device_code}
        S-->>C: 400 authorization_pending OR 200 {token}
    end
    C->>C: write token to config.toml (0600)
    C-->>U: reminder: export SPRAWL_AGENT_SECRET
